## 📖 What It Does

Image Arranger is a browser-based collage/layout tool. You upload images, then freely position, resize, rotate, crop, filter, and annotate them on an **A4-sized canvas** (794×1123px). When done, you export everything as a PNG, JPG, or PDF. It supports **multiple pages** so you can build multi-page documents.

